Umm... de ca 40 avsnitten som aldrig visades innan serien lades ned lämnade aldrig storyboardstadiet... Tror du på allvar att Nickelodeon skulle lägga ned pengar på 40 avsnitt och sen aldrig visa dem? Att en serie läggs ned betyder inte att man slutar visa den, utan att man slutar producera den...

Nick cancelled the show because it didn't score very well with their primary audience, probably because it was slightly too weird. It has however sold more merchandise than any other series they have aired, which suggests that it might not have been cancelled if they had aimed their customer survey to people above age eleven...

The crew were allowed to finish the christmas episode, even though it was supposed to air after several episodes that never got animated. That's why mini-moose suddenly appears, he was scheduled to join Zim in one of those episodes. That is also the reason for Zim's slightly cryptic "Yep, been with me the whole time..."
